    "title": "Front Office Manager - Scootsy - Attractive Package",
    "description": "We at Scootsy are looking for an experienced Front Office Manager based out of Pune. If you are a result-oriented professional with a passion for excellence, we want to hear from you.\n\nAbout Scootsy:\nScootsy is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Assist in menu planning, costing, and food festival coordination\n• Develop and maintain relationships with corporate clients\n• Monitor F&B service quality and maintain hygiene standards\n• Coordinate housekeeping and maintenance for room readiness\n• Conduct regular guest satisfaction surveys and implement improvements\n• Manage reservations and optimize room revenue through yield management\n• Plan and execute banquets, events, and MICE functions\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• CA / CMA / CFA certification\n• 0-1 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in F&B Service\n• Proficiency in Tour Planning\n• Proficiency in Crisis Management\n• Proficiency in OTA Management\n• Proficiency in Barista Skills\n• Proficiency in Front Office\n• Proficiency in MICE\n• Proficiency in GDS Systems\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Salary Range: 2.5 LPA - 6 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Pune, Maharashtra, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Scootsy!",
